store.name: store
store.short_desc: Get a cache store instance by name.

repository.name: repository
repository.short_desc: Create a new cache repository with the given implementation.

getDefaultDriver.name: getDefaultDriver
getDefaultDriver.short_desc: Get the default cache driver name.

setDefaultDriver.short_desc: Set the default cache driver name.

extend.name: extend
extend.short_desc: Register a custom driver creator Closure.

has.name: has
has.short_desc: Determine if an item exists in the cache.

get.short_desc: Retrieve an item from the cache by key.

many.name: many
many.short_desc: Retrieve multiple items from the cache by key.
many.long_desc: Items not found in the cache will have a null value.

pull.name: pull
pull.short_desc: Retrieve an item from the cache and delete it.

put.name: put
put.short_desc: Store an item in the cache.

putMany.name: putMany
putMany.short_desc: Store multiple items in the cache for a given number of minutes.

add.name: add
add.short_desc: Store an item in the cache if the key does not exist.

increment.name: increment
increment.short_desc: Increment the value of an item in the cache.

decrement.short_desc: Decrement the value of an item in the cache.

forget.name: forget
forget.short_desc: Remove an item from the cache.

tags.name: tags
tags.short_desc: Begin executing a new tags operation if the store supports it.

setDefaultCacheTime.name: setDefaultCacheTime
setDefaultCacheTime.short_desc: Set the default cache time in minutes.

offsetExists.name: offsetExists

offsetGet.name: offsetGet
offsetGet.short_desc: Retrieve an item from the cache by key.
